=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
צידן    - צידון / tsîydôn  tsîydôn / tsee-done', tsee-done'
=== Etymology ===

From [[צוּד]] {{HH|6679}} in the sense of catching fish; [[fishery]]; 
=== Proper noun ===
Tsidon, the name of a son of Canaan, and of a place in [[Palestine]]: - [[Sidon]], [[Zidon]].